Jarkell Ravensteel<br>
Firiona Vie <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umonkeybass.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MonkeyBass</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/30/02 7:03:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11670.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Newbie Hate Raid</span><hr size=1> Say what? This most reent patch added a new mob there? Could you post some info on it?<br>
